ARROWMAP 是一款轻量级的浏览器导航新标签页，它能让您快速精准地在网页间穿梭

🚀 快速访问- 一键直达您最常用的网站，告别繁琐的地址栏输入
🎯 精准搜索- 强大的书签搜索功能，想找就找，一搜即得
🎨 简约设计- 清爽的界面设计，不干扰正常浏览体验


ARROWMAP is a lightweight browser navigation newtab extension that helps you move between web pages with arrow-like precision and speed. Through intelligent bookmark management, it makes web browsing more efficient than ever before.

🚀 Quick Access - Instantly reach your most visited websites with a single click, eliminating tedious URL typing
🎯 Precise Search - Powerful bookmark search functionality lets you find exactly what you're looking for, instantly
🎨 Minimalist Design - Clean, uncluttered interface that won't interfere with your browsing experience
